Welcome to [i]Rocket Adventures[/i]!

Probably the first time you will play Rocket League in an Isometric environment, there are 20 levels to beat in this game.
It's not simple but not too hard, i made it quite accessible to everyone.

[Dpad] - Skip/Change Level
[Ballcam button] Switch near/far cameras 


Join my discord if you have any questions, issues, or just want to discuss with me :)
